ComicInfo.Title: Chapter 12
ComicInfo.Series: Archer Coe and the Thousand Natural Shocks
ComicInfo.Summary: Once upon a time, Archer Coe was a neophyte hypnotist working at a dingy nightclub and pulling short cons. Long before his troubles with the police and the mysterious murder of Jack Midland, Archer was a key performer in an entirely different reality. Who are the other players in this forgotten mystery, and how did it get Archer Coe into the pickle that's currently threatening to drive him mad?
